            . I am an officer. I found this parcel on the prisoner about eight o'clock last Monday morning, about one hundred and fifty yards from his master's house; I asked where he was going with them: he said to a Mr. Hoffner's, a cooper, for his master; he told me who his master was, and we went back there.</p>
               <p>The prisoner pleaded distress.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 43.</p>
